      "content": "i've tried the professionals. i've tried every pill and every therapy. nothing actually stops the sensation. it just feels like i'm being punished every second of every day. sometimes i just sit here thinking... wouldn't it be more merciful to just not be? like, if the pain is permanent, isn't the only real relief just... stopping? it feels like the only logical way to find any peace.",
